    <string name="about_me_text">This is Gyasi Story \n\n Gyasi Story is a native Floridian.  He was born in Fort Lauderdale, Florida and moved to Orlando, Florida at the age of five.  In 2006 He graduated from Florida Southern College with a BS in Computer Information Systems.  Upon completing FSC he began his career in technology education, directing courses in various subject from programming to web design.  He also spent his spare time creating websites for various small businesses and non-profit organizations. In 2009 he was certified as a Master Certified Internet Webmaster Designer to help his credentials a freelance web developer.  Gyasi has always enjoyed the challenge of helping student rise to their true potential.</string>
